          <li><a href data-target=".jumbo .tab-source-view" data-toggle="pill">Design / Source View</a></li>
        </ul>

        <div class="tab-content">
          <p class="tab-panel tab-general active fade in">
            Our BPMN 2.0 compliant standalone modeling tool. Built with simplicity and modeling only in mind.
          </p>
          <p class="tab-panel tab-model-outline fade">
            Quickly navigate through bigger process diagrams using the model outline.
          </p>
          <p class="tab-panel tab-context-pad fade">
            Use the context pad to change task, gateway and event types or to continue modeling from where you are.
          </p>
          <p class="tab-panel tab-source-view fade">
            Switch to the source view to get all the details hidden in the underlaying BPMN 2.0 xml. Change the source and synchronized it back into the design view.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="download">
          <a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="./download/" role="button">Download camunda Modeler</a>
        </p>

        <p>
          Version <%= release.version %>, available for <a href="./download/#windows">Windows</a>, <a href="./download/#linux">Linux</a> and <a href="./download/#macos">Mac OS</a>
        </p>
